    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Thanks, I've dug into it a bit. `IPython.core.shellapp.InteractiveShellApp._run_cmd_line_code` is what runs the file in question, but it's `IPython.core.interactiveshell.InteractiveShell.safe_execfile` that calls the method to show the traceback. There's a `tb_offset` parameter to drop frames from the top of the traceback, but I'll need to work out what's the right place to set it.\n"
